    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Bug: when managing the state of InstantSearch externally, several identical queries were sent to Algolia. \r\n\r\nRoot cause: The componentWillReceiveProps hook of React gets called for both the InstantSearch root component and the widgets. But since we don't check for the props equality we're doing a new search even if their props are still the same.\r\n\r\n",
    "created_at": "2016-11-28T15:15:51Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/1612#issuecomment-263297011",
